74
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:41,280
She'd have to greet you every day

75
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,280
and bring your foot bath.

76
00:03:42,740 --> 00:03:44,280
So, you also believe the Young Marshal

77
00:03:44,280 --> 00:03:45,760
would marry several women?

78
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,560
Families of such standing

79
00:03:48,560 --> 00:03:50,560
often have a few concubines.

80
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:54,400
But I think the Young Marshal
only has eyes for you.

81
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,600
Gray.

82
00:03:58,600 --> 00:04:00,400
Do you believe what she said?

83
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:03,000
I sure don't.

84
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,960
Madam...

85
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,160
You just recovered.

86
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:09,920
You still need more bed rest.

87
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,960
I'm fine.

88
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,360
I just wanted to take a walk

89
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,760
and get some fresh air.

90
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,920
I saved your life this time.

91
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,840
Don't you owe me one?

92
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,200
Alright.

93
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,640
I want to join the army.

94
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,320
I want to be your combat medic.

95
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:27,520
No way.

96
00:04:28,320 --> 00:04:30,040
Miss Su is highly skilled

97
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,200
and has great ambition.

98
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,400
If she can take care of you

99
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,680
as a combat medic,

100
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,040
