105
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:53,240
I'll head out first.

106
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,400
Wait.

107
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,360
Did Wanwan upset you?

108
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,880
No.

109
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,200
Then why won't you even look at me?

110
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,880
What did she tell you?

111
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,920
Miss Su is selfless.

112
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,720
Whatever she says is right.

113
00:05:38,690 --> 00:05:40,080
I'm just being petty.

114
00:05:48,800 --> 00:05:50,000
I think you're sulking.

115
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,200
No.

116
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:53,260
You're feeling wronged.

117
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:54,720
No.

118
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,880
And maybe a little jealous.

119
00:05:58,200 --> 00:05:59,200
Not at all.

120
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:07,840
In my heart,

121
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,800
I don't care about selflessness.

122
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,640
I only care about my wife.

123
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,400
Stop saying things like that.

124
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,520
Alright.

125
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:23,200
Grandma wants us to take
wedding photos tomorrow.

126
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,960
She says it's for a keepsake.

127
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,700
We'll go in the morning.

128
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:30,000
- I don't want to.
- That's an order.

129
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,440
I'm not your soldier.

130
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,360
It's Grandma's order.

131
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,200
Alright.

